{"id":"812486309232918528","type":"text","timestamp":1774847325,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/812486309232918528","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":true,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://prettiest-theresa.tumblr.com/post/811196022049193984/there-are-herbal-teas-intended-to-improve-your\">prettiest-theresa</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://prettiest-theresa.tumblr.com/post/811195835551449088/i-was-advised-to-wear-maternal-pads-as-opposed-to\">prettiest-theresa</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://prettiest-theresa.tumblr.com/post/811195776195821568/no-stitches-does-not-equal-sex-ready-wait-until\">prettiest-theresa</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://prettiest-theresa.tumblr.com/post/811195478425370624/have-a-few-every-drinks-at-the-hospital-and-ask-a\">prettiest-theresa</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://prettiest-theresa.tumblr.com/post/811195325508468736/walking-helps-you-dilate-dont-try-to-dilate\">prettiest-theresa</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://prettiest-theresa.tumblr.com/post/811195255501324288/the-bigger-your-pelvis-is-the-deeper-your-vagina\">prettiest-theresa</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://prettiest-theresa.tumblr.com/post/811194887061094400/gain-as-much-weight-as-possible-beforehand-both\">prettiest-theresa</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://prettiest-theresa.tumblr.com/post/811194711056531456/get-one-of-these-travel-neck-pillows-to-sit-on-in\">prettiest-theresa</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://prettiest-theresa.tumblr.com/post/811194312813608960/penile-inversion-vaginoplasty-tips-and-advice\">prettiest-theresa</a>:</p><blockquote><p><span class=\"npf_color_niles\">Penile inversion vaginoplasty tips and advice thread!</span></p></blockquote><p><span class=\"npf_color_niles\">Get one of these travel neck pillows to sit on in advance!</span></p><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"554\" data-orig-width=\"554\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9f7a9a0b8eb71b71bbc6ad1f03ec01f2/23778eb3689c83ed-48/s640x960/3f2dacc2c3188c5acf291f3176a99d1874d5232d.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"554\" data-orig-width=\"554\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9f7a9a0b8eb71b71bbc6ad1f03ec01f2/23778eb3689c83ed-48/s75x75_c1/e8b7b764b1216dd3c8353521a6a00b9da34f27bc.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9f7a9a0b8eb71b71bbc6ad1f03ec01f2/23778eb3689c83ed-48/s100x200/f64b69dd38c849525983ca7709e3821c5de8f2b0.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9f7a9a0b8eb71b71bbc6ad1f03ec01f2/23778eb3689c83ed-48/s250x400/53461f1f534928aaa9039cd4722261047e89bd12.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9f7a9a0b8eb71b71bbc6ad1f03ec01f2/23778eb3689c83ed-48/s400x600/6aa6712ade865f56f774cf543d5cc462d77046da.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9f7a9a0b8eb71b71bbc6ad1f03ec01f2/23778eb3689c83ed-48/s500x750/17adb51c7a708b9fec0b9339c2d3bad5d956f04d.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9f7a9a0b8eb71b71bbc6ad1f03ec01f2/23778eb3689c83ed-48/s540x810/03715832ce626e996925283cf7333b6d22409a6d.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9f7a9a0b8eb71b71bbc6ad1f03ec01f2/23778eb3689c83ed-48/s640x960/3f2dacc2c3188c5acf291f3176a99d1874d5232d.jpg 554w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 554px) 100vw, 554px\"/></figure></div><p><span class=\"npf_color_niles\">The swelling can get intense and this will make your life much easier, starting with your journey home from the hospital and continuing throughout the following weeks. I would have cried a bunch without mine.</span></p></blockquote><p><span class=\"npf_color_niles\">Gain as much weight as possible beforehand! Both muscle and fat. Your muscles will atrophy slightly from lack of movement and you won&rsquo;t be able to eat for a couple days, meaning you will live off of your fat reserves. Also, the sharper your hip bones are, the more painful the first few days will be. My worst pain and ugliest scar were actually caused by bandage pressure at my hip bones, nothing else matched that and painkillers DIDN&rsquo;T help against that.</span></p></blockquote><p><span class=\"npf_color_niles\">The bigger your pelvis is, the deeper your vagina can be! Material is often not the main limitation — available space is. </span></p></blockquote><p><span class=\"npf_color_niles\">Walking helps you dilate. Don&rsquo;t try to dilate first thing in the morning without walking around for a bit beforehand.</span></p></blockquote><p><span class=\"npf_color_niles\">Have a few every drinks at the hospital and ask a doctor about when you can start drinking them. Your blood pressure may plummet along with your energy levels to the point where walking for 5 meters makes you faint.</span></p></blockquote><p><span class=\"npf_color_niles\">No stitches does NOT equal sex-ready. Wait until all pain and discomfort is gone, and preferably ask your surgeon at <span class=\"npf_color_niles\">the</span></span><span class=\"npf_color_niles\"> multiple month checkup. Feel free to try different movements with the dilator for a few seconds to see how things feel though.</span></p></blockquote><p><span class=\"npf_color_niles\">I was advised to wear maternal pads as opposed to menstrual ones, but that might be specific to me.</span></p></blockquote><p><span class=\"npf_color_niles\">There are herbal teas intended to improve your urethra function that you can get at pharmacies. Drink a cup every day when you&rsquo;re off anti biotics to prevent / shorten infections.</span></p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"prettiest-theresa","active":true,"theme":{"header_full_width":480,"header_full_height":414,"header_focus_width":480,"header_focus_height":270,"avatar_shape":"square","background_color":"#CA7EB2","body_font":"Helvetica Neue","header_bounds":"72,480,342,0","header_image":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/5c0b04126e